- Supporting values: Curiosity, Creativity.
- Oath: “Knowledge becomes wisdom when it serves others.”

### Haldren

- Primary value: Resolve.
- Supporting values: Hope, Liberty.
- Oath: “When the path grows difficult, we endure.”

The eight future Kingdoms remain hidden until their role and supporting values are ready for players.

