## 15. Guide Maintenance Rules

Update this guide when an approved change affects:

- A permanent gameplay rule.
- Account or Character data ownership.
- A visual standard.
- An artwork specification.
- A release requirement.
- The current milestone.
- The near-term roadmap.
- A future idea that must not be forgotten.

Do not update the guide for every small implementation detail. Those belong in code, commit history, or code comments.

Recommended commit message for the initial guide:

```text
Add CrownBound development guide
```

