Kingdom Standing progression

Kingdom Standing belongs to the permanent account.
“Member” is the initial Standing after swearing a Kingdom Oath.
Standing will later advance through the established rank list.
Stats and Kingdom pages must read the Standing from the same account data.
Until progression is implemented, the UI may display the temporary default Standing of “Member.”

